name: Derekdoingstuff.GitHub.io
body:
This is a basic page to show off this great org which allows me to have all of my github accounts interact with eachother for my projects.

Popping in with my other account just to show that I can edit this stuff on the fly and easily between the accounts.

-Derek Hearn
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
